Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: ravioli
Version: 0.3.0
Summary: Checks for spaghetti code
Home-page: https://github.com/ElectronVector/ravioli
Author: Matt Chernosky
Author-email: matt@electronvector.com
License: MIT
Platform: UNKNOWN

A tool for calculating simple, useful complexity metrics -- notably the Koopman Spaghetti Factor (KSF) -- for C. This tool is designed to work especially on embedded software written for compilers with non-standard extensions. It works without a compiler or any preprocessing required.


